                            <comment id="15058322" author="iamaleksey" created="Tue, 15 Dec 2015 16:58:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;AbstractType&lt;/tt&gt; import does seem to be redundant, but +1 to the patch, so long as cassci is happy.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
